#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: surcharge.php
msgid "Surcharge - Checkout Fees for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Recargo: tarifas de pago para WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: surcharge.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/surcharge/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/es/surcharge/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: surcharge.php
msgid "Add fixed or percentage fees to the WooCommerce cart and checkout."
msgstr ""
"Añade tarifas fijas o porcentuales al carrito y al pago (checkout) de "
"WooCommerce."

#. Author of the plugin
#: surcharge.php
msgid "WPPoland.com"
msgstr "WPPoland.com"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: surcharge.php
msgid "https://wppoland.com"
msgstr "https://wppoland.com"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:62 src/Admin/Settings.php:63
msgid "Surcharge"
msgstr "Recargo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:101
msgid "Active"
msgstr "Activo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:103
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Desactivado"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:110
msgid "Add checkout fees in two steps"
msgstr "Añade tarifas de pago en dos pasos"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid ""
"1. Add a fee row below. 2. Choose a fixed amount or a percentage of the "
"cart. Fees appear in the cart, at checkout and on the order."
msgstr ""
"1. Añade una fila de tarifas a continuación. 2. Elige una cantidad fija o un"
" porcentaje del carrito. Las tarifas aparecen en el carrito, al finalizar la"
" compra y en el pedido."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:119
msgid "General"
msgstr "General"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:124
msgid "Enable fees"
msgstr "Habilitar tarifas"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:129
msgid "Apply the fees below at cart and checkout."
msgstr ""
"Aplique las siguientes tarifas en el carrito y en el momento del pago."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:131
msgid ""
"Master switch. When off, no fees are added to any cart, regardless of the "
"rows below."
msgstr ""
"Interruptor maestro. Cuando está desactivado, no se agregan tarifas a ningún"
" carrito, independientemente de las filas a continuación."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:140
msgid "Fees"
msgstr "Tarifas"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:141
msgid "Each row is one fee. A fee with no label is skipped."
msgstr "Cada fila es una tarifa. Se omite una tarifa sin etiqueta."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:145 src/Admin/Settings.php:159
msgid "Add fee"
msgstr "Añadir tarifa"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:187
msgid "Fee"
msgstr "Tarifa"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:191
msgid "Label"
msgstr "Etiqueta"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:192
msgid "e.g. Handling fee"
msgstr "p.ej. Tarifa de manejo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:193
msgid ""
"The wording customers see on the cart, checkout and order. Leave blank to "
"skip this row."
msgstr ""
"El texto que los clientes ven en el carrito, en el pago y en el pedido. "
"Déjelo en blanco para omitir esta fila."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:197
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:199
msgid "Fixed amount"
msgstr "Cantidad fija"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:200
msgid "Percentage of cart"
msgstr "Porcentaje del carrito"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:202
msgid ""
"Fixed adds the same amount every order. Percentage scales with the cart "
"subtotal."
msgstr ""
"Fijo añade la misma cantidad en cada pedido. El porcentaje escala con el "
"subtotal del carrito."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:206
msgid "Amount"
msgstr "Cantidad"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:209
msgid "Charged in your store currency, e.g. 3.50."
msgstr "Se cobra en la moneda de su tienda, p. 3,50."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:210
msgid "A percentage from 0 to 100, e.g. 2.5 adds 2.5% of the subtotal."
msgstr "Un porcentaje de 0 a 100, p.e. 2,5 suma el 2,5% del subtotal."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:223
msgid "Receipt line"
msgstr "linea de recibo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:230
msgid "Taxable"
msgstr "sujeto a impuestos"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:232
msgid ""
"On: tax is calculated on this fee using your standard rate. Off: the fee is "
"added tax-free."
msgstr ""
"Activado: el impuesto se calcula sobre esta tarifa utilizando tu tipo "
"estándar. Desactivado: la tarifa se añade sin impuestos."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:239
msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Habilitado"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:240
msgid "Off keeps the row saved but stops charging it."
msgstr "Con «Desactivado», la fila se guarda pero deja de cobrarse."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:242
msgid "Remove fee"
msgstr "Eliminar tarifa"

#: surcharge.php:47
msgid ""
"Surcharge - Checkout Fees for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be active."
msgstr ""
"Recargo: las tarifas de pago de WooCommerce requieren que WooCommerce esté "
"activo."
